\mathbb C^n
\forall x,z\in\mathbb C^n
d(x,z)\geq0
d(x,z)=0
x=z
d(x,z)=||x-z||=(\sum_{j=1}^{n}|x_j-z_j|^2)^\frac{1}{2}\geq0.
